                <title ref="" xml:lang="en">Bk. II</title>
                <note>slightly imperfect at the beginning, part of the index of contents being
                  lost.* It treats of the different kinds of soils; the crops suitable for
                  each;</note>
                <note>The first leaf has been restored to the volume since De Lagarde's text
                  was"published. See Land, Anecd. Syr., t.i., p. 18.</note>
              </msItem>
